#
# EfiPay: registre a URL com ?webhook_token=<WEBHOOK_SECRET>
#   Exemplo: https://seusite.com/webhook/efipay?webhook_token=<WEBHOOK_SECRET>
#
# Melhor Envio: configure o header no painel do ME:
#   Authorization: Bearer <WEBHOOK_SECRET>
